label: Siuslaw News
title: Siuslaw_News
exrest: The Siuslaw News is a semiweekly newspaper published in Florence, Oregon, United States, since 1904. The News covers western Lane County, from the Pacific Ocean to Deadwood and Greenleaf, and from Yachats on the north to Gardiner on the south. The paper was previously known as the Siuslaw Oar and The West. It is published on Wednesdays and Saturdays by the News Media Corporation and has a circulation of 4,000.
